{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Bearstone Campsite is a first-person horror game that follows the journey of our character who goes missing during a camping trip.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Maria, Paul, and Nathan should have never gone without you. It\u2019s absurd they thought they could manage without the only sensible person in the group. But could they, really? Your friends are out there, desperate, waiting for you to come back.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323740/extras/tabela2.gif?t=1739387413\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Now, witness their story. You left them to this fate.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You\u2019ve always been cautious... or maybe just a coward. But this time, what are you going to do?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323740/extras/walk.gif?t=1739387413\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>There is NO ONE coming to save you!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You may feel a presence behind you. But there\u2019s no one here in charge, no one to help. And don't count on your phone working, either.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323740/extras/lamphead.gif?t=1739387413\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Prepare yourself for the Silence of the Night.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From the dense depths of the forest, through the tunnels of the sewers, to the cold, empty corridors of the factory... you must be strong enough to survive each step.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323740/extras/silah2.gif?t=1739387413\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Stay quiet!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pray that Manbear and Howler don\u2019t hear you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>You can\u2019t leave until you find your friends.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Being alone out here might just kill you. Stay sharp, stay calm, what you see may unsettle you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Good luck.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323740/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739387413","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323740/page.bg.jpg?t=1739387413","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323740/f838d2ffeebcab00ae89f1ec54e5a35f8365813e/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739387413","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323740/f838d2ffeebcab00ae89f1ec54e5a35f8365813e/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739387413","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Captions available","id":13},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"HDR available","id":61}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"Bearstone Campsite includes depictions of dismembered human limbs, dismemberment of imaginary creatures, minor and severe injuries, and the use of weapons."},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Bearstone Campsite is a first-person horror game that follows the journey of our character who goes missing during a camping trip.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Maria, Paul, and Nathan should have never gone without you. It\u2019s absurd they thought they could manage without the only sensible person in the group.